{"_type":"post","_id":"nursing-assistant-night-shift-income-increase","title":"看護助手の夜勤で得られる手当と実際の収入アップ例","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"nursing-assistant-night-shift-income-increase"},"excerpt":"看護助手の夜勤手当は、月々の収入を大きく増やすチャンスです。この記事では、夜勤手当の種類や計算方法を具体的に解説し、夜勤をこなすことでどれくらい収入がアップするのか、リアルな例を交えてご紹介します。あなたの収入アップの参考にしてください。","body":[{"_key":"key01","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"看護助手の仕事は、日勤だけでなく夜勤も選択肢の一つです。夜勤は体力的な負担がある一方で、夜勤手当が支給されるため、効率的に収入を増やすことができます。ここでは、夜勤で得られる手当の種類と、実際の収入アップ例をご紹介します。"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"key02","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"もくじ"}],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"key03","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当の種類と計算方法"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"number","level":1},{"_key":"key04","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当による収入アップの具体例"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"number","level":1},{"_key":"key05","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当を最大限に活用するためのポイント"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"number","level":1},{"_key":"key06","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"まとめ"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"number","level":1},{"_key":"key07","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当の種類と計算方法"}],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"key08","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当は、主に以下の種類があります。"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"key09","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[["strong"]],"text":"深夜手当："},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" 労働基準法で定められており、22時から翌朝5時までの勤務に対して、通常の賃金の25%以上が上乗せされます。"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key10","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[["strong"]],"text":"夜勤手当（施設独自）："},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" 多くの施設で、深夜手当とは別に、夜勤1回につき固定額が支給されます。相場は1回あたり5,000円から10,000円程度です。"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key11","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[["strong"]],"text":"休日夜勤手当："},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" 休日（法定休日や所定休日）に夜勤を行った場合に、さらに上乗せされる手当です。"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key12","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当による収入アップの具体例"}],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"key13","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"ここでは、月給18万円の看護助手が夜勤手当によってどれくらい収入が増えるか、具体的な例を見てみましょう。"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"key14","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[["strong"]],"text":"例1：月4回の夜勤の場合（週1回程度）"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"key15","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"基本給：180,000円"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key16","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当（1回8,000円と仮定）：8,000円 × 4回 = 32,000円"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key17","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"総支給額：212,000円（手取り約17万円）"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key18","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[["strong"]],"text":"例2：夜勤専従の場合（月8回夜勤）"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"key19","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"基本給：180,000円"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key20","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当（1回8,000円と仮定）：8,000円 × 8回 = 64,000円"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key21","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"総支給額：244,000円（手取り約20万円）"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key22","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"夜勤手当を最大限に活用するためのポイント"}],"style":"h2"},{"_key":"key23","_type":"block","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[["strong"]],"text":"夜勤手当が高い施設を選ぶ："},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" 求人情報を比較し、夜勤手当の金額が高い施設を選ぶことで、効率的に収入を増やせます。"}],"style":"normal","listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_key":"key24","_type":"block",